@startuml
title Utilities - Level 1

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

package "Reusable helpers" {
	class Traits
	class Flags
	class CachedData
	class Contracts
	class BinaryField
}

package "Used by library systems" {
	class Widgets
	class Input
	class Rendering
	class Threads
}

Widgets --> Traits : activation and ownership behavior
Input --> Contracts : event subscriptions
Rendering --> CachedData : rebuild only when dirty
Threads --> Contracts : safe delayed notifications
Rendering --> Flags : option sets
BinaryField --> Rendering : structured bytes when needed

note bottom
Utilities are not a separate feature for beginners.
They are reusable building blocks used by the larger systems.
end note

@enduml
